# 强制 GitHub Linguist 将仓库语言识别为 Java
*.java linguist-language=Java

# 将非核心语言文件标记为 vendored/文档，降低对语言统计的影响
*.md linguist-documentation
*.ps1 linguist-vendored
*.cmd linguist-vendored
Dockerfile linguist-vendored
docker-compose.yml linguist-vendored
*.yml linguist-vendored
*.xml linguist-vendored
*.html linguist-vendored

# 将辅助目录标记为 vendored（脚本、静态资源），不影响 Java 统计
scripts/* linguist-vendored
src/main/resources/static/* linguist-vendored